message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product, which has been meticulously designed and crafted to exceed your expectations. This exceptional item not only boasts high-quality materials but also innovative features that promise to enhance your daily experience. Given its unique features and the care put into its creation, I believe it's worth more than $150. Considering its value and the benefits it offers, I kindly propose a price of $200 for this product. I look forward to your consideration and hope we can reach an agreement that satisfies both of us.
